                <ul>
                  <li>Conduct daily cleaning and disinfection of the lab (at least daily, and more frequently if feasible).</li>
                  <li>Keep cleaning logs that include date, time and scope of cleaning.</li>
                  <li>Conduct frequent disinfecting of heavy transit areas and high-touch surfaces in the lab (e.g., doorknobs, handrails).</li>
                  <li>In event of a positive case, notify researchers that WPI has shut down the site for a deep cleaning and disinfecting by the EHS HAZMAT team.</li>
                  <li>Clean shared spaces (e.g., conference rooms, shared equipment) between use and supply cleaning products (e.g., sanitizer, disinfecting wipes).  Please contact EHS if you need assistance in procuring such supplies.</li>

